@INDEX MAIN

@NODE MAIN "The Arexx-Interface"
@{u}@{b}The Arexx-Interface@{uu}@{ub}

The Arexx-port  of the program is named ChaosPro.Rexx.  Several commands aren't
implemented,  because I  don't want  to waste time for something, which perhaps
nobody uses. So if you really use it and miss some commands,  don't hesitate to
suggest them to me.


The following commands are implemented:
@{"About" LINK "About"}                        @{"GetActPicture" LINK "GetActPicture"}                  @{"Recalc" LINK "Recalc"}
@{"AddFractal" LINK "AddFractal"}                   @{"GetAttr" LINK "GetAttr"}                        @{"Redo" LINK "Redo"}
@{"BoxZoom" LINK "BoxZoom"}                      @{"GetColor" LINK "GetColor"}                       @{"RefreshParms" LINK "RefreshParms"}
@{"CalcFract" LINK "CalcFract"}                    @{"GetPicture" LINK "GetPicture"}                     @{"RGBToHSV" LINK "RGBToHSV"}
@{"ChangeFractName" LINK "ChangeFractName"}              @{"GetScreenDepth" LINK "GetScreenDepth"}                 @{"SavePicData" LINK "SavePicData"}
@{"ChangePaletteName" LINK "ChangePaletteName"}            @{"HSVToRGB" LINK "HSVToRGB"}                       @{"SavePicture" LINK "SavePicture"}
@{"ChoiceRequest" LINK "ChoiceRequest"}                @{"IsTask" LINK "IsTask"}                         @{"SetAttr" LINK "SetAttr"}
@{"CloseAnim1" LINK "CloseAnim1_2"}                   @{"LoadPicData" LINK "LoadPicData"}                    @{"SetColor" LINK "SetColor"}
@{"CloseAnim2" LINK "CloseAnim1_2"}                   @{"MakeNewUndo" LINK "MakeNewUndo"}                    @{"SetPalette" LINK "SetPalette"}
@{"CloseDataWindow" LINK "CloseDataWindow"}              @{"MakeProportional" LINK "MakeProportional"}               @{"SetShowJul" LINK "SetShowJul"}
@{"ClosePalette" LINK "ClosePalette"}                 @{"Move" LINK "Move"}                           @{"SetShowLoc" LINK "SetShowLoc"}
@{"ClosePalWork" LINK "ClosePalWork"}                 @{"OpenAnim1" LINK "OpenAnim1_2"}                      @{"SetTaskPri" LINK "SetTaskPri"}
@{"CloseParm1" LINK "CloseParm1"}                   @{"OpenAnim2" LINK "OpenAnim1_2"}                      @{"SetToDefault" LINK "SetToDefault"}
@{"CloseParm2" LINK "CloseParm2"}                   @{"OpenDataWindow" LINK "OpenDataWindow"}                 @{"ShowHelp" LINK "ShowHelp"}
@{"CloseParm3" LINK "CloseParm3"}                   @{"OpenPalette" LINK "OpenPalette"}                    @{"StopCalc" LINK "StopCalc"}
@{"CloseParms3D1" LINK "CloseParms3D1"}                @{"OpenPalWork" LINK "OpenPalWork"}                    @{"SystemInfo" LINK "SystemInfo"}
@{"CloseParms3D2" LINK "CloseParms3D2"}                @{"OpenParm1Window" LINK "OpenParm1Window"}                @{"Undo" LINK "Undo"}
@{"CloseParms3D3" LINK "CloseParms3D3"}                @{"OpenParm2Window" LINK "OpenParm2Window"}                @{"WindowFallback" LINK "WindowFallBack"}
@{"CloseShowJulWindow" LINK "CloseShowJulWindow"}           @{"OpenParm3Window" LINK "OpenParm3Window"}                @{"WindowType" LINK "WindowType"}
@{"CloseShowLocWindow" LINK "CloseShowLocWindow"}           @{"OpenParms3D1Window" LINK "OpenParms3D1Window"}             @{"Zoom" LINK "Zoom"}
@{"CloseUserWindow" LINK "CloseUserWindow"}              @{"OpenParms3D2Window" LINK "OpenParms3D2Window"}
@{"Colorcycling" LINK "Colorcycling"}                 @{"OpenParms3D3Window" LINK "OpenParms3D3Window"}
@{"ContinueCalc" LINK "ContinueCalc"}                 @{"OpenShowJulWindow" LINK "OpenShowJulWindow"}
@{"DelCalced" LINK "DelCalced"}                    @{"OpenShowLocWindow" LINK "OpenShowLocWindow"}
