@NODE Colorcycling "Colorcycling"

@{b}NAME@{ub}
Colorcycling

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
Colorcycling ON/S OFF/S UPWARDS/S DOWNWARDS/S SPEED/K/N

@{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
Controls colorcycling...

@{b}INPUT PARAMETERS@{ub}
ON        : If given, ColorCycling is switched on
OFF       : If given, ColorCycling is switched off
UPWARDS   : If given, cycling is done in direction to higher colorregisters.
DOWNWARDS : same as before, but downwards
SPEED     : If given, the number after that defines the cycling speed.
            10 is fast, 50 is slow...

@{b}RESULTS@{ub}
RC:
  8  ... Keyword 'Speed' given, but no number after that
 10  ... unknown keyword
Result:
 N.A.

@{b}BUGS@{ub}
---

@{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
---

@ENDNODE

