@NODE Undo "Undo"

@{b}NAME@{ub}
Undo

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
Undo <Fractalname>

@{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
Undoes the last change. Internally there's a list with all the changes made. With
'Undo' you step back through this list, with 'Redo' you step forward.

@{b}INPUT PARAMETERS@{ub}
<Fractalname> : Name of the fractal

@{b}RESULTS@{ub}
RC:
 5 ... fractal unknwon
 8 ... wrong number of parameters
Result:
 N.A.

@{b}BUGS@{ub}
---

@{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
@{"Redo" LINK "Redo"}

